Module HackathonManagementSystem

Package model

package model
  • Class
    Description
    Category
    Enumeration of hackathon competition categories.
    Competitor
    The Competitor class models an individual team member participating in the hackathon.
    HackathonTeam
    The HackathonTeam class represents a team participating in the National-Level Hackathon competition.
    Judge
    The Judge class represents a hackathon judge who evaluates and scores teams.
    Name
    The Name class stores an individual's first and last name in a structured format.
    ReportGenerator
    Generates formatted reports for hackathon teams, displayed via console output.
    Score
    The Score class represents the scoring components assigned to a hackathon team by judges.
